                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers. Winds west to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-05-05T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-06T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-04T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-05T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Medium chance of showers, most likely in the early morning. Winds west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light in the late afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 7 and 10 with daytime temperatures reaching around 18.</text>
                <text type="fire_danger">No Rating</text>
                <text type="uv_alert">##</text>
